msgid ""
"A small concealed holster worn on the ankle.  It is awkward to use without "
"practice.  Activate to holster/draw a small pistol."
msgstr "一種佩戴在腳踝上的小型隱蔽槍套。未經練習使用起來會有些笨拙。激活以收槍/拔出一把小口徑手槍。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_holster.json
