msgstr "一塊已屈服於血肉的大石頭。"

#. ~ Description for flesh
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"Disgusting mounds of meat, slimy and organic as it seems to live. This "
"pinkish flesh is rotten to the core, and setting it on fire may not be the "
"cure."
msgstr "令人作嘔的肉堆，滑膩而有生機，彷彿活著。這粉紅色的血肉從核心腐爛，點燃它可能並非解決之道。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\omt.json
msgid "flesh wall"
msgstr "血肉牆"

#. ~ Description for flesh wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"Disgusting wall of meat, slimy and organic as it seems to live. This compact"
" lumps of flesh is sinister to the core, and setting it on fire may not be "
"the cure."
msgstr "令人作嘔的肉牆，滑膩而有生機，彷彿活著。這團緊實的肉塊從核心透著邪惡，點燃它可能並非解決之道。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "vein wall"
msgstr "脈絡牆"

#. ~ Description for vein wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "A wall composed of vein-like tendrils, seemingly made on the fly."
msgstr "一堵由靜脈狀觸鬚構成的牆壁，似乎是臨時形成的。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "splook!"
msgstr "噗嚕！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "flesh bed"
msgstr "肉質床鋪"

#. ~ Description for flesh bed
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A lump of flesh carefully molded into a bed. Although it may be sticky, "
"it'll keep you warm."
msgstr "一塊精心塑造成床鋪的肉塊。雖然可能有些黏膩，但能保暖。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "floor residue"
msgstr "地面殘留物"

#. ~ Description for floor residue
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A gaping mouth on the floor. Good for storing items, just don't fall into "
"it."
msgstr "地面上一個張開的嘴巴。適合存放物品，只是別掉進去。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "residue"
msgstr "殘留物"

#. ~ Description for residue
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A gaping mouth protruding from the floor. Great for storing items, just "
"don't go inside it."
msgstr "一張從地面突出的血盆大口。非常適合存放物品，只是別走進去。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "flesh rack"
msgstr "血肉貨架"

#. ~ Description for flesh rack
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "Lay your items here. Worry not, they won't dissolve."
msgstr "將物品放置於此。別擔心，它們不會溶解。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "flesh container"
msgstr "血肉容器"

#. ~ Description for flesh container
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A large sack of flesh for storing liquids, with a vented suction point for "
"ease of use."
msgstr "一個用於儲存液體的大型血肉袋，帶有通風吸口以便使用。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "bioluminescent wart"
msgstr "生物發光疣"

#. ~ Description for bioluminescent wart
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "This bulbous clump of warts emit bioluminescent lights."
msgstr "這團球狀疣簇會發出生物熒光。"

