"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster builds at the marked spot.'"
msgstr ""
"由怪物施放的法術。如果你看到這條信息，請改為閱讀以下內容：\n"
"'施法者在標記位置進行建造。'"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Challenge - Crimson Horror' for a male character
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_scen.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Challenge - Crimson Horror"
msgstr "挑戰 - 猩紅恐怖"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Challenge - Crimson Horror' for a female character
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_scen.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Challenge - Crimson Horror"
msgstr "挑戰 - 猩紅恐怖"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Challenge - Crimson Horror' for a male
#. character.
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_scen.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"The pungent aroma of uncooked  meat insults your nostrils as soon as your "
"mind wakes. The ground seemingly pulses in a macabre rhythm and when opening"
" your eyes, you're met with a horrible sight! The forest you once knew is "
"covered in red, cyst-like growths. Thoughts race through your mind but one "
"sticks out: \"How am I gonna get out of this mess?\""
msgstr ""
"意識甦醒的瞬間，生肉的刺鼻氣味便侮辱著你的鼻腔。地面彷彿以詭異的節奏脈動，睜開雙眼，你目睹了駭人的景象！曾經熟悉的森林被紅色囊腫般的增生覆蓋。思緒在腦海中飛馳，但有一個念頭格外突出：“我該如何擺脫這團糟？”"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Challenge - Crimson Horror' for a female
#. character.
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_scen.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"The pungent aroma of uncooked  meat insults your nostrils as soon as your "
"mind wakes. The ground seemingly pulses in a macabre rhythm and when opening"
" your eyes, you're met with a horrible sight! The forest you once knew is "
"covered in red, cyst-like growths. Thoughts race through your mind but one "
"sticks out: \"How am I gonna get out of this mess?\""
msgstr ""
"意識甦醒的瞬間，生肉的刺鼻氣味便侮辱著你的鼻腔。地面彷彿以詭異的節奏脈動，睜開雙眼，你目睹了駭人的景象！曾經熟悉的森林被紅色囊腫般的增生覆蓋。思緒在腦海中飛馳，但有一個念頭格外突出：“我該如何擺脫這團糟？”"

#. ~ Starting location for scenario 'Challenge - Crimson Horror'.
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_scen.json
msgctxt "start_name"
msgid "Flesh Forest"
msgstr "血肉森林"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh weaving'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_skills.json
msgid ""
"Your skill in manipulating the flesh.  A higher skill allows for faster "
"repair and crafting of flesh-based items."
msgstr "你操縱血肉的技能。更高的技能允許更快地修復和製作基於血肉的物品。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_skills.json
msgid "bio-organic weapons"
msgstr "生物有機武器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bio-organic weapons'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_skills.json
msgid "Your efficiency over flesh weapons that your body morphs into."
msgstr "你對身體變形而成的血肉武器的掌控效率。"

